<br>
The Chardok raid tonight is to get me the note from the Overking for the cleric epic. The idea is to stay for another King after that (2 hour re-spawn) and get at least a second note, which will be lottoed amongst all clerics in the raid who still need it.<br>
<br>
The rest of the loot will be lottoed following our standard NBG rules (everyone who can and WILL USE the item can roll for it, one item per person per raid unless it's a default. Spells don't count as regular loot, but if you get a spell don't expect to get two :)<br>
<br>
Kikulle is puller<br>
Colubridae is Main Assist and Raid Leader<br>
Linila is Secondary Assist<br>
Tempestade is Lotto Captain and Raid Leader<br>
<br>
Some Tips:<br>
----------<br>
Please stay off shouts unless you're in the pull group<br>
Set your assist keys ahead of time, you break a mez, you may get 48 people killed. How does that look on your resume? :)<br>
Group Leaders please be quick in changing your groups when it's Overking time<br>
Everyone PLEASE print the groups and have them next to you, I will not keep repeating group formation everytime someone asks<br>
To reduce lag, I suggest turning off particles, PC names, spell effects, everything you can.<br>
We are meeting in Burning Woods at 7:45 PM EST. We are moving in no later than 8:15 PM EST. If you are not there by this time, don't bother coming.<br>
I said we are meeting in Burning Woods, outside the Sarnak Fort. That is NOT in Chardok zone or the DL/BW zone. If you don't know how to get there, get a map.<br>
<br>
Thanks all for signing up, I think we will have a very funny and successfull evening.<br>
